Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,--------main--------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.11,0:00:09.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.18,0:00:17.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,言叶…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.52,0:00:42.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诚…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.87,0:01:06.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是说了  没法立刻回去的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.00,0:01:09.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么啊  料理都已经做好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.13,0:01:12.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到时又得重新热了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.72,0:01:15.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说  不要管我  你自己先吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.09,0:01:18.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诚根本不明白这个含义
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.92,0:01:25.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…为了能和你一起吃  才努力做的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.03,0:01:27.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你那么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.60,0:01:36.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.38,0:01:36.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.40,0:01:39.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么不想吃我做的料理吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.87,0:01:41.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是那样的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.62,0:01:42.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.99,0:01:44.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么不愿意回来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.10,0:01:48.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是说了  有些事不方便离开
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.12,0:01:50.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.93,0:01:51.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.88,0:01:53.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诚  你现在和谁在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.94,0:01:55.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有和谁…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.95,0:01:57.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看你说话的语气  你又要花心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.21,0:02:00.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是啦  我这里的事也很棘手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.28,0:02:03.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我说了让你给我解释一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.01,0:02:06.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.50,0:02:07.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看  支支吾吾了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.21,0:02:12.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你有点自觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.90,0:02:15.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的什么都不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.60,0:02:22.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我肚子里…有诚的孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.51,0:02:25.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明没跟言叶说过这件事…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.26,0:02:28.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等…等等
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.91,0:02:31.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么现在要提桂同学的名字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.21,0:02:35.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诚？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.03,0:02:38.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说  难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.05,0:02:41.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桂同学在那里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.09,0:02:45.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诚？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.54,0:02:47.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要怀上孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.96,0:02:51.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要在大家面前说出来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.80,0:02:53.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然跟我说怀了孩子什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.58,0:02:55.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不知道该怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.38,0:02:56.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诚…诚  等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.80,0:02:58.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  我不听了  给我回去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.84,0:03:01.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别自以为是我女朋友就随便赖在我家里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.07,0:03:18.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.79,0:03:27.80,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我就先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.74,0:04:00.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20}模手原坂下到了  模手原坂下到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.87,0:04:27.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍等一下  我这就去泡茶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.97,0:04:48.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想和我一起吃…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.07,0:04:56.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一开始是只要看着她就满足了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.11,0:05:00.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是坐在她旁边一起吃午饭就会很紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.45,0:05:03.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是从什么时候开始的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.50,0:05:07.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要抚摸她  想要抱紧她
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.81,0:05:13.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经不能满足于只拥有这些
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.76,0:05:17.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要更多  更多…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.01,0:05:25.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就因为我的任性…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.86,0:05:27.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  烫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.68,0:05:38.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.27,0:05:42.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.88,0:05:51.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么桂同学会出现在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.18,0:05:53.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界…为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.03,0:05:55.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.74,0:05:57.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你和桂同学在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.18,0:05:59.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.06,0:06:00.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.00,0:06:03.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你别再缠着诚了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.02,0:06:06.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的  世界
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.48,0:06:07.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么不对的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.29,0:06:10.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没有和桂同学分手吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.08,0:06:14.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都已经怀上你的孩子了  就要这么甩掉我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.87,0:06:15.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.85,0:06:19.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诚  你已经不喜欢桂同学了不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.42,0:06:20.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.60,0:06:24.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是你主动叫她来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.60,0:06:27.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桂同学做过什么了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.48,0:06:29.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,言…言叶她…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.66,0:06:31.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么都没…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.56,0:06:32.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.47,0:06:35.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是桂同学要诚带你来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.49,0:06:37.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我滚出去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.79,0:06:38.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滚出去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.06,0:06:45.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勾引诚君的不是西园寺同学吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.91,0:06:46.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.82,0:06:47.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,言叶…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.93,0:06:54.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了拆散我和诚君  才做了那样的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.09,0:06:58.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对  我和诚是相爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.89,0:07:00.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们彼此的感情是相通的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.79,0:07:03.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是你一厢情愿的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.92,0:07:04.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.91,0:07:11.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,清浦同学其实只是你拜托她的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.50,0:07:13.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刹那？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.64,0:07:15.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刹那怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.64,0:07:18.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托她…是什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.07,0:07:21.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.03,0:07:24.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来你不知道啊  西园寺同学
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.95,0:07:26.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.00,0:07:32.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,清浦同学  也是喜欢诚君的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.75,0:07:33.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.89,0:07:38.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来那不是为了让我放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.34,0:07:41.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是清浦同学真正的心意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.26,0:07:46.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别随口胡说了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.11,0:07:51.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刹那是我的…好…好朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.76,0:07:56.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别看我这样  也是很宽容的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.82,0:07:59.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种程度的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.27,0:08:01.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就原谅你们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.91,0:08:02.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.23,0:08:05.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西园寺同学说过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.58,0:08:10.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诚非常疼我的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.22,0:08:18.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以  我也必须要多为诚君考虑考虑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.68,0:08:22.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事到如今…还说这话…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.80,0:08:24.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我终于明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.53,0:08:28.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诚君总是在我身边等着我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.62,0:08:32.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,言叶…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.76,0:08:33.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.02,0:08:38.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会再犹豫了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.55,0:08:56.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.86,0:09:00.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.61,0:09:21.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要——！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.68,0:09:37.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是上次那个关于他的调查
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.17,0:09:39.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,名字是伊藤诚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.93,0:09:41.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.46,0:09:44.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生日是10月16日  血型是O型
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.44,0:09:47.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.52,0:09:52.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在入学式就向你伸出援手  这不是个很浪漫的邂逅吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.38,0:09:53.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说明你们很有缘呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.43,0:09:57.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他的也问来了不少哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.02,0:10:00.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊藤果然是个不错的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.00,0:10:02.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大体的评价是良好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.54,0:10:05.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.55,0:10:07.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后  照片也拍来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.48,0:10:08.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.60,0:10:11.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也给刹那传过去好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.03,0:10:19.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.98,0:10:26.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而  你却把打算摘给别人的花自己留下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.35,0:10:30.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后看到他的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.12,0:10:34.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却为了自己能得到赞扬而把花送给了他
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.44,0:10:35.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.09,0:10:39.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「能找到这么漂亮的花  我是个好孩子吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.81,0:10:44.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来告诉你怎样去摘得那朵花吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.60,0:10:49.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像这样假装亲切  好好炫耀自己一番
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.61,0:10:50.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.84,0:10:53.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以花为借口来接近他
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.25,0:10:55.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伪君子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.69,0:10:58.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的  不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.24,0:10:59.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没想过要这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.57,0:11:02.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那为什么世界会去做那种事？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.56,0:11:04.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.73,0:11:13.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且  如果世界没有坐在伊藤的旁边
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.44,0:11:19.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果世界没有把桂同学介绍给诚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.35,0:11:23.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许就不会发生这样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.37,0:11:31.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的——！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.21,0:11:41.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的…因为诚他说…这样就好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.38,0:11:45.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要有我就好了…其他人都不需要…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.30,0:11:46.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要有我就好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.80,0:11:50.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.81,0:11:52.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.98,0:11:53.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.94,0:12:15.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.25,0:12:25.35,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,言叶说会帮你介绍一家熟悉的医院
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.49,0:12:29.30,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,据说早点打掉的话对身体的负担也会小一些
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.55,0:13:09.56,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}我有话想当面对你说  到你家去吧  就我们两个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.74,0:13:14.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.51,0:13:18.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西园寺同学决定要去医院了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.56,0:13:20.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  大概吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.43,0:13:23.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也是多亏了言叶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.35,0:13:25.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  没什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.51,0:13:33.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然很好喝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.65,0:13:36.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个是特制的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.27,0:13:39.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是  是妈妈亲传的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.82,0:13:45.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今后我想像这样一直和言叶在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.53,0:13:49.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很容易被周围环境所左右
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.24,0:13:53.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前真的做了很多对不起言叶的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.98,0:13:58.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但从今以后  我的眼中只有言叶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.34,0:14:00.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诚君…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.70,0:14:13.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个…先坐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.74,0:14:26.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个的结果怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.01,0:14:34.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.57,0:14:48.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去给你泡茶好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.30,0:14:49.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去泡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.50,0:15:03.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界果然是铁了心了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.53,0:15:04.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.90,0:15:44.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是说  要去他那一起做饭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.50,0:15:44.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.62,0:15:47.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在他那过一夜  然后明天去海边吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.17,0:15:49.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,游艇好棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.13,0:15:52.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心也要一起去嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.33,0:15:53.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.06,0:15:55.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.36,0:16:02.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.91,0:16:04.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.96,0:16:05.96,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an5}对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.99,0:16:15.09,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}永别了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.04,0:16:26.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.60,0:16:39.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你休想…休想一个人去和桂同学过幸福日子！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.15,0:16:59.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.87,0:18:41.19,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,600)}我在屋顶等你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.82,0:19:09.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,医院你去过了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.12,0:19:12.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里的医生很厉害的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.94,0:19:15.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.24,0:19:17.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.68,0:19:20.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…我不想去你介绍的医院
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.54,0:19:24.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是骗人…的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.72,0:19:31.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想让诚君回心转意  才骗他说怀了他的孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.49,0:19:32.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.02,0:19:34.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么不对呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.16,0:19:36.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.64,0:19:39.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么就应该好好地去医院检查下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.78,0:19:47.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且  西园寺同学也不可能怀上他的孩子嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.51,0:19:53.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为诚君的女朋友  是我才对嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.75,0:19:54.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.74,0:19:55.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.00,0:20:01.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想…我也想做诚的女朋友啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.03,0:20:03.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明只是这样而已…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.60,0:20:06.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明一直都在强迫自己去满足诚所想的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.95,0:20:08.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么…为什么啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.61,0:20:13.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诚君的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.58,0:20:15.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.38,0:20:18.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诚君的话  就在这里哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.44,0:20:20.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不妨问问他怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.41,0:20:53.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西园寺同学说的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.58,0:21:02.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们来检验下到底是真是假吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.46,0:21:43.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.62,0:21:47.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是在说谎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.22,0:21:53.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里面根本没有孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.49,0:22:30.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于只有我们两个人了呢  诚君
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,--------IN--------
